{"tid":2034772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家覺得攬炒到最後最黑暗既時刻會係點？","createTime":"2020-05-25T12:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T12:37:09.000Z","uid":41389,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3fd870a133e2114ca7fdfa9903ebaf3d202cf704","tid":2034772,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T12:34:58.000Z","msg":"解放軍？<br />\n我覺得攬炒到最後中共會對香港進行種族大清洗 <br />\n用新疆篤灰模式藍絲篤黄絲再關入集中營思想教育<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未撚到個一刻 都唔會知未來會有幾撚恐怖<br />\n亦都唔好以為咩都唔做唔會搞到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遲早搞到你 如果你係無能力移民 <br />\n你而家唔反抗 係到笑鳩勇武送頭 比軍師利用<br />\n他日亦都唔使止意反抗"},{"pid":"bf70ce4c2931c54ce3fb977a7bb0ce5197e74bff","tid":2034772,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T12:35:44.000Z","msg":"自由誠可貴 返工價更高<br />\n若為移民顧 兩者皆可拋"},{"pid":"2f8bcaf4e27d054196ec0daab1144b297bf901b8","tid":2034772,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T12:35:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"171a3d3456cbb131fa84609b53102dcfc07db794","tid":2034772,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T12:37:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">攬炒咗你咪知囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"}]}